
          Scenario-08
           "Pursuit"<clsr>
  Ledin succeeded at driving
Lance from Anzel Fortress and
protecting Albert.
  After the battle, Albert chose
to join Ledin in his fight, and
thus the entourage grew one man
stronger.<clsr>
  Commander Zaldaff, of the
Dalshis army, retreated to meet
up with their other forces.
  Seeing this as an opportunity,
Ledin began a hot pursuit of
the enemy.<clsr>
Winning Conditions
- Defeat of Lord Zaldaff

Losing Conditions
- Death of Ledin
- Escape of Lord Zaldaff<clsr>
